text: Paralepetopsis tunnicliffae is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Neolepetopsidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== northeastern Pacific Ocean == Habitat == hydrothermal vents ==References== ==External links== * Category:Neolepetopsidae Category:Gastropods described in 2008
title: Paralepetopsis tunnicliffae
